<title>GERMANY: Daimler 1996 consolidated operating data.</title>
<headline>Daimler 1996 consolidated operating data.</headline>
<dateline>STUTTGART, Germany 1997-04-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year to December 31, 1996</p>
<p>(in millions of marks unless stated)</p>
<p>    Division passenger cars profit	 3,100  vs n/a</p>
<p>    Division commercial vehicles loss    400    vs n/a</p>
<p>    Division aerospace loss		  196    vs 7,220 loss</p>
<p>    Division services profit		 288    vs 112 profit</p>
<p>    Division directly managed bus. loss  585    vs 2,216 loss</p>
<p>Daimler also issued the following information on one-off charges to operating profit:</p>
<p>    Provisions on AEG and  Fokker	  0	vs 3.8</p>
<p>    Write-offs on investments, good-will 0	vs 2.9</p>
<p>    Structural expenditures		  1.1    vs 1.4</p>
<p>NOTE - Full name of the German industrial group is Daimler-Benz AG. These figures reflect consolidated operating data.</p>
<p>--Frankfurt Newsroom, +49 69 756525</p>
